high_descs: Take a step to the left and face the sink on the right.
Pick up the egg from the left side of the sink.
Hold the egg and take a step to the right, and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the egg inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the egg and shut the door.
Carry the egg and turn around and face the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and place the egg inside. Shut the door.
Walk to the sink on the left side.
Pick up the the potato from the sink.
Move over to the sink on the right side and look up above the sink at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the potato in the microwave to the right of the white mug, close the door, heat up the potato, take the potato out of the microwave, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the potato in the fridge, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the potato and put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the egg out of the left sink.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and look up at the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take the egg out and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk forward, then right and walk up to the fridge.
Put the heated egg inside the fridge on the second shelf from the top, then close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the fridge.
